6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to environment and natural resources;
creating the Environment and Natural Resources
8 Efficiency Act of 2026; providing for
noncodification; and providing an effective date.
9
10
11
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
14 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
15 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Environment and
16 Natural Resources Efficiency Act of 2026".
17 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
